creator: Julia Caroline Dorr
description:
LibriVox recording of The Sonnets by Julia Caroline Dorr.
Read in English by DannyHauger; Newgatenovelist; Renkotsu; Crln Yldz Ksr; Vetta; Sarah Sellari; SkyAlbatross; Domenica Campbell
This is a collection of Julia Caroline Dorr's Sonnets, from her collected poems. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
